statements: SELECT * FROM performance_reports;
SELECT supplier_id, report_date, metrics FROM performance_reports WHERE report_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT report_id, report_date, outcomes FROM performance_reports WHERE supplier_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001';
SELECT supplier_id, metrics FROM performance_reports WHERE report_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT report_id, outcomes FROM performance_reports WHERE supplier_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002';
SELECT * FROM performance_reports WHERE supplier_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT report_id, report_date FROM performance_reports WHERE report_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT supplier_id, COUNT(*) FROM performance_reports GROUP BY supplier_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT report_id, metrics->>'clicks' AS clicks FROM performance_reports WHERE metrics @> '{
'clicks': '100'}' ORDER BY clicks DESC;
SELECT supplier_id, MAX(report_date) FROM performance_reports GROUP BY supplier_id ORDER BY MAX(report_date) DESC;
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance_reports;
SELECT supplier_id, report_date, total_sales FROM supplier_performance_reports ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT supplier_id, total_sales FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE total_sales > 10000;
SELECT supplier_id, total_expenses FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE total_expenses < 5000 ORDER BY total_expenses ASC;
SELECT supplier_id, report_date, total_sales, total_expenses FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE supplier_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE total_sales > 1000 AND total_expenses < 500
SELECT supplier_id, report_date FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE report_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY report_date DESC
SELECT supplier_id, AVG(total_sales) AS average_sales FROM supplier_performance_reports GROUP BY supplier_id HAVING AVG(total_sales) > 500
SELECT s.supplier_id, sd.performance_rating FROM supplier_performance_reports AS s INNER JOIN supplier_dashboards AS sd ON s.supplier_id = sd.supplier_id WHERE sd.performance_rating >= 8
SELECT supplier_id, dashboard_date, issues_found FROM supplier_dashboards WHERE issues_found IS NOT NULL ORDER BY dashboard_date ASC
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance;
SELECT supplier_name, total_revenue FROM supplier_performance ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
SELECT supplier_name, total_orders, total_revenue FROM supplier_performance WHERE total_orders > 100 ORDER BY total_orders DESC;
SELECT supplier_name, total_orders, total_revenue FROM supplier_performance WHERE supplier_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM order_details JOIN supplier_performance ON order_details.supplier_id = supplier_performance.supplier_id;
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance ORDER BY total_revenue DESC, total_orders ASC;
SELECT supplier_name, total_revenue FROM supplier_performance WHERE total_orders > 100 ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
SELECT supplier_name, total_orders, total_revenue FROM supplier_performance WHERE supplier_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY total_orders DESC, total_revenue ASC;

SELECT supplier_name, revenue, orders_count FROM supplier_performance JOIN performance_metrics ON supplier_performance.supplier_id = performance_metrics.supplier_id WHERE performance_metrics.year = 2021 ORDER BY revenue DESC;

SELECT supplier_name, order_date, order_amount FROM supplier_performance JOIN order_details ON supplier_performance.supplier_id = order_details.supplier_id WHERE order_amount > 500 ORDER BY order_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance_metrics;
SELECT supplier_id, order_count FROM supplier_performance_metrics WHERE rating > 4.5;
SELECT order_date, delivery_date, order_status FROM order_details ORDER BY order_date DESC;
SELECT supplier_id, contact_name FROM supplier_contacts WHERE contact_email LIKE '%@example.com';
SELECT dashboard_id, report_type, dashboard_url FROM performance_dashboard;
SELECT * FROM supplier_performance_metrics ORDER BY supplier_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT supplier_id, order_count, delivery_performance FROM supplier_performance_metrics WHERE delivery_performance > 0.8 ORDER BY delivery_performance DESC;
SELECT supplier_id, order_count, rating FROM supplier_performance_metrics WHERE order_count > 100 ORDER BY rating DESC;

SELECT supplier_contacts.contact_name, supplier_contacts.contact_email, performance_dashboard.report_type FROM supplier_contacts INNER JOIN performance_dashboard ON supplier_contacts.supplier_id = performance_dashboard.supplier_id;
SELECT supplier_id, SUM(order_count) AS total_orders FROM supplier_performance_metrics GROUP BY supplier_id HAVING total_orders > 500 ORDER BY total_orders DESC;
SELECT supplier_id, report_date, delivery_performance, quality_performance FROM supplier_performance_reports;
SELECT metric_name, metric_description FROM dashboard_metrics WHERE metric_id = 1;
SELECT tracking_date, tracking_value FROM key_metrics_tracking ORDER BY tracking_date DESC;
SELECT outcome_name, outcome_status FROM outcomes_tracking WHERE outcome_status = 'completed';
SELECT tool_id, tool_name, tool_type FROM visualization_tools WHERE tool_type = 'chart';

SELECT supplier_id, report_date FROM supplier_performance_reports WHERE delivery_performance > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM key_metrics_tracking WHERE tracking_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT tool_name, tool_type FROM visualization_tools WHERE tool_type = 'Dashboard';
